Press 3.5 and decided to release it as a plugin on WordPress.org. Mainly, this meant writing a README (and creating a proper repo for it on GitHub). This is a simple one-trick-pony plugin – it adds a Preview button to the fullscreen editor toolbar. Nothing more, nothing less. If you’ve been up late [&hellip;]\'>Alex King: Fullscreen Editor Preview Button for WordPress</a></li></ul></div>','no');
