INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (1,1,'2012-06-14 14:46:14','2012-06-14 14:46:14','<span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">As we mentioned in the About Us page, we starting making these bags not long ago, basing the design on a 1960s purse found while cleaning out an estate. We developed a few prototypes and then asked for feedback from friend, relatives and anybody else we could get to weigh in.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">We got recommendations to add longer straps so the bag could be carried on a shoulder, add pockets to the bags, and make them larger. All great suggestions that we are taking to heart and may add in future bags.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">We\'ve also received suggestions to make the bags in bright colors, add rhinestones and other adornments, and dress them up. In other words, give the bags some \"bling.\" That\'s the question we are grappling with now. The original bag was designed to be rustic chic, like Minnetonka loafers and Native American beadwork. It\'s in that spirit that we designated the names of the the bags after places in America with Indian names.</span>\r\n\r\nDo we keep the bags rustic or design them with more punch? Now it\'s your turn to weigh in and give us feedback. What would you like to see in  newly designed bags?','To Bling or Not to Bling?','','publish','open','open','','hello-world','','','2013-01-22 16:33:28','2013-01-22 20:33:28','',0,'http://wpengine.com/?p=1',0,'post','',1);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (2,2,'2012-06-20 08:16:48','2012-06-20 12:16:48','<a href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/home-2/sewing-material-2-bags/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-174\"><img class=\"alignright\" alt=\"sewing-material-2-bags\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/sewing-material-2-bags-150x150.png\" width=\"90\" height=\"90\" /></a>\r\n<h2>Our Product Selection</h2>\r\nThese relaxed yet sophisticated handbags offer style and everyday functionality. They are the perfect-size to handle the essentials, such as a phone, small wallet, comb, glasses and lipstick.\r\n\r\nThe size of the bag is perfect for a quick shopping trip. For a longer day, it\'s small and flexible and will easily fit in your briefcase or tote and keep all your essentials in one place.\r\n\r\nAll bags are carefully handcrafted and fully lined. They measure approximately 8 inches high and 5-1/2 inches across and weigh only a few ounces. Purse feet and a reinforced bottom allow bag to stand upright. Drawstring closure doubles as a wrist strap.\r\n<h2><b>The Sequoia</b><a href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/sample-page/sequoia-bag-3/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2145\"><img class=\" wp-image-2145 alignright\" alt=\"sequoia-bag\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/sequoia-bag2-150x150.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></h2>\r\nThis buttery deerskin bucket bag is stylish and just the right size to hold all the essentials. Shown in brown and natural deerskin. You’ve got to feel it to appreciate how soft it is! You are sure to get many compliments when you carry this bag.\r\n<h2><b>The Algonquin</b><a href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/sample-page/bw-bag-2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2141\"><img class=\" wp-image-2141 alignright\" alt=\"BW-bag\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/BW-bag1-150x150.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></h2>\r\nThis relaxed yet sophisticated handbag offers style and everyday functionality. Shown in cream and black leather. The size of this bag is perfect carry on a quick outing or move it from briefcase to tote and keep all your essentials in one place.\r\n<h2><b>The Tahoe</b><a href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/sample-page/tahoe-bag-2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2139\"><img class=\" wp-image-2139 alignright\" alt=\"tahoe-bag\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/tahoe-bag1-150x150.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></h2>\r\n<p align=\"left\">This casual and carefree bag is handy for any outing. Shown in denim and brocade, this bag is nature-friendly, since no animal products are used in its production.</p>\r\n\r\n<h2><b>The Niagara</b><a href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/sample-page/bridal-bag-3/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2142\"><img class=\" wp-image-2142 alignright\" alt=\"bridal-bag\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/bridal-bag1-150x150.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></h2>\r\n<p align=\"left\">This bag is perfect for a busy bride. It can hold lip gloss, small sprays, phone, money, feminine items and a handkerchief—all the things a bride needs on her big day. Shown in faux silk moiré fabric, adorned with beaded fringe and satin flowers. This is a perfect bridal shower gift.</p>\r\nThese bags also make excellent gifts for your bridesmaids and wedding party. Ask us about special requests to match bridal gowns.\r\n<p align=\"left\"></p>','westcoast / east handbags styles','','publish','closed','closed','','sample-page','','','2013-01-23 21:13:13','2013-01-24 01:13:13','',0,'http://demo2.woothemes.com/artificer/?page_id=2',0,'page','',0);
