INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (2170,2,'2013-01-09 21:23:40','2013-01-10 01:23:40','<h3>How We Got Started</h3>\n<a href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/about/original-bag/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2182\"><img class=\"alignright\" alt=\"leather drawstring bag\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/original-bag-300x300.png\" width=\"240\" height=\"240\" /></a>West Coast/East Bags got its start in 2012 when Gail Carrigan rediscovered an adorable handbag that her mother carried everywhere in the 1960s. She loved the bag, but let’s say it was a “little worn.” She decided to remake a bag for herself and then for her sisters. And there the design instinct kicked in. Why not create the bag in different materials, including leather, denim, brocade and wedding dress material?\n\nWhat has been just as important to Gail as developing the perfect essentials bag, is ensuring that every every bag is produced to the highest quality standards and that every customer is entirely satisfied with her bag.\n\nWest Coast/East sources all materials in the US, and attempts to reuse materials, including denim jeans, brocade upholstery samples, and bridal dresses.\n\nGail was born in New Jersey, moved west to the San Francisco Bay Area at a young age, and then returned east to the Boston Area in 2000. Design influences from the West Coast and East Coast – as well as an interest in artisan craft – come together in these bags.\n\nWest Coast / East, is an artisan handmade accessories business, specializing in distinctive accessories for eclectic and discerning women.\n\nWe are always happy to hear your comments and feedback. Please contact us at 781.728.9190 or at gacarrigan@westcoast-east.com.\n\nMany thanks for visiting our site!\n\n&nbsp;','About Us','','inherit','closed','closed','','76-autosave','','','2013-01-09 21:23:40','2013-01-10 01:23:40','',76,'http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/76-autosave/',0,'revision','',0);
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES (2171,2,'2013-01-06 20:44:32','2013-01-07 00:44:32','<a href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/home-2/sewing-material-2-bags/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-174\"><img class=\"alignright\" alt=\"sewing-material-2-bags\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/11/sewing-material-2-bags-150x150.png\" width=\"90\" height=\"90\" /></a>\n<h2>Our Products</h2>\nThese relaxed yet sophisticated handbags offer style and everyday functionality. They are the perfect-size to handle the essentials, such as a phone, small wallet, comb, glasses and lipstick.\n\nThe size of the bag is perfect for a quick shopping trip. For a longer day, it\'s small and flexible and will easily fit in your briefcase or tote and keep all your essentials in one place.\n\nAll bags are carefully handcrafted and fully lined. They measure approximately 8 inches high and 5-1/2 inches across and weigh only a few ounces. Purse feet and a reinforced bottom allow bag to stand upright. Drawstring closure doubles as a wrist strap.\n\n&nbsp;\n<h3><b>The Sequoia</b><a href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/sample-page/sequoia-bag-3/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2145\"><img class=\" wp-image-2145 alignright\" alt=\"sequoia-bag\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/sequoia-bag2-150x150.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></h3>\nThis buttery deerskin bucket bag is stylish and just the right size to hold all the essentials. Shown in brown and natural deerskin. You’ve got to feel it to appreciate how soft it is! You are sure to get many compliments when you carry this bag.\n\n&nbsp;\n<h2><b>The Algonquin</b><a href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/sample-page/bw-bag-2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2141\"><img class=\" wp-image-2141 alignright\" alt=\"BW-bag\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/BW-bag1-150x150.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></h2>\nThis relaxed yet sophisticated handbag offers style and everyday functionality. Shown in cream and black leather. The size of this bag is perfect carry on a quick outing or move it from briefcase to tote and keep all your essentials in one place.\n<h2><b>The Tahoe</b><a href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/sample-page/tahoe-bag-2/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2139\"><img class=\" wp-image-2139 alignright\" alt=\"tahoe-bag\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/tahoe-bag1-150x150.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></h2>\n<p align=\"left\">This casual and carefree bag is handy for any outing. Shown in denim and brocade, this bag is nature-friendly, since no animal products are used in its production.</p>\n\n<h3><b>The Niagara</b><a href=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/sample-page/bridal-bag-3/\" rel=\"attachment wp-att-2142\"><img class=\" wp-image-2142 alignright\" alt=\"bridal-bag\" src=\"http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/bridal-bag1-150x150.png\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\" /></a></h3>\n<p align=\"left\">This bag is perfect for a busy bride. It can hold lip gloss, small sprays, phone, money, feminine items and a handkerchief—all the things a bride needs on her big day. Shown in faux silk moiré fabric, adorned with beaded fringe and satin flowers. This is a perfect bridal shower gift.</p>\nThese bags also make excellent gifts for your bridesmaids and wedding party. Ask us about special requests to match bridal gowns.\n<p align=\"left\"></p>','West Coast / East Handbag Designs','','inherit','closed','closed','','2-autosave','','','2013-01-06 20:44:32','2013-01-07 00:44:32','',2,'http://gacarrigan.wpengine.com/2-autosave/',0,'revision','',0);
